  "special": {
    "title": "Itchy. Tasty.",
    "description": "Fires slow, slightly arcing corrosive shots that explode on impact and deal splash damage. Projectiles also self-detonate after about 0.85 seconds, making long-range use unreliable. Red text: Itchy. Tasty. Always corrosive. Greatly increased status chance and status damage, but heavily reduced projectile damage."
  },
  "notes": "Explosions add 80% of weapon damage as splash, and this bonus is affected by grenade damage boosts. If a shot auto-detonates at maximum flight rather than hitting something, the splash radius is 20% larger. With a Siren, 5/5 Flicker plus a class mod that adds +5 Flicker can reach 100% corrosive status chance. A Witch class mod combined with an Elemental relic or a Bone of the Ancients can also reach 100% status chance, though it offers fewer extra perks than Legendary Siren.",
